### Upload Service — REST Client test file
### Requires VS Code extension: REST Client (humao.rest-client)
###
### Prerequisites:
###   1. docker compose -f infra/docker-compose.yml up -d postgres minio rabbitmq
###   2. pnpm nx run upload-service:serve
###
### Auth: service trusts X-User-Id set by gateway — no JWT needed here

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8086
@base    = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/upload
@userId  = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@userId2 = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002

# Fill in after creating a draft / submitting
@draftId  = REPLACE_WITH_DRAFT_ID
@trackId  = REPLACE_WITH_TRACK_ID
@objectKey = REPLACE_WITH_OBJECT_KEY
@jobId    = REPLACE_WITH_JOB_ID

###
### ─── HEALTH ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [1] Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###
### ─── SINGLE TRACK FLOW ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [2] Create SINGLE draft (thumbnail optional)
POST {{base}}/drafts
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

My New Track
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="genre"

POP
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="release_type"

SINGLE
------FormBoundary--

### [3] Get presigned PUT URL for audio
GET {{base}}/drafts/{{draftId}}/tracks/{{trackId}}/audio-url?filename=my_song.mp3
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### [4] Confirm audio (after client PUT to MinIO using uploadUrl)
POST {{base}}/drafts/{{draftId}}/tracks/{{trackId}}/confirm
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "objectKey": "{{objectKey}}"
}

### [5] Submit draft → creates upload job → transcoder picks it up
POST {{base}}/drafts/{{draftId}}/submit
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###
### ─── ALBUM FLOW ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [6] Create ALBUM draft
POST {{base}}/drafts
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

My Debut Album
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="genre"

ROCK
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="release_type"

ALBUM
------FormBoundary--

### [7] Add Track 1 to album
POST {{base}}/drafts/{{draftId}}/tracks
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Opening Act",
  "trackNumber": 1
}

### [8] Add Track 2 to album
POST {{base}}/drafts/{{draftId}}/tracks
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Big Closer",
  "trackNumber": 2
}

### [9] Get audio URL for a track
GET {{base}}/drafts/{{draftId}}/tracks/{{trackId}}/audio-url?filename=track1.flac
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### [10] Delete a track
DELETE {{base}}/drafts/{{draftId}}/tracks/{{trackId}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###
### ─── DRAFT MANAGEMENT ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [11] Get draft details
GET {{base}}/drafts/{{draftId}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### [12] Cancel draft
POST {{base}}/drafts/{{draftId}}/cancel
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### [13] Try cancelling a submitted draft (expects 409)
POST {{base}}/drafts/{{draftId}}/cancel
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### [14] No auth (expects 401)
GET {{base}}/drafts/{{draftId}}

###
### ─── JOB MONITORING ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [15] List all jobs
GET {{base}}/jobs
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### [16] List jobs filtered by status
GET {{base}}/jobs?status=TRANSCODING&page=1&size=10
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### [17] Get job by ID
GET {{base}}/jobs/{{jobId}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### [18] Retry failed job
POST {{base}}/jobs/{{jobId}}/retry
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### [19] Cancel job
POST {{base}}/jobs/{{jobId}}/cancel
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
